  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7430849/" class="title-link">世界是个隐喻</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7430849"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/arlmy/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2171815-18.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/arlmy/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">绝缘儿</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-03-31"
      class="main-meta">2015-03-31 23:08:20</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7430849_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  用两个早上的时间读完了，读后的第一感觉是：玄妙。没有什么比一本充满真相的书更可怕，也没有什么比充满诗意的真相更美妙。  生命的诗性， 世界是隐喻  联想到上周看电影《邮差》里有这样一句台词，邮差向聂鲁达发问：“所以整个世界对于其他事物都是隐喻？”这是一句能让人愣...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7430849/#comments">(9回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">90有用 / 10没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7430849_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7430849_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
