  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7427995">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7427995/" class="title-link">万物千门</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7427995"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/Stewart/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1018146-30.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Stewart/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">锡兵</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-03-28"
      class="main-meta">2015-03-28 22:32:29</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7427995_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  《万物 创世》的主线是讲述宇宙学、地质学、古生物学视角下宇宙诞生到人类出现前的世界，但它并非纯粹的科普读物。作者同时吸收了历史和现实中宗教、文学、艺术等非科学领域对相关主题的阐释和演绎，并把所有这些内容以同题并列的方式组合到了一起。他的内心一定是一个博物学者...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7427995/#comments">(10回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">76有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7427995_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7427995_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
